data.description: Come see this beautiful, well maintained 4 bed 2.5 bath home located in Surrey Hills! Open concept floor plan with 20+ ft ceilings in entry and living room. Just off the entry is a nice size office with french doors.  Built in surround sound in living room and Updated painting throughout the house. Master suite on first level with dual vanities, separate soaking tub and shower, & walk-in closet.  Upstairs you will find a big game room/bonus room, three nice size bedrooms and a full bathroom. In-ground sprinkler system and 2 wired speakers on the back patio. Nice neighborhood park.  Located a mile away from the Surrey Hills Golf Club and close to the turnpike, NW Expressway and shopping. Ready for you to move in! Also includes a 10 year transferable warranty for roof and foundation
